column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.l,p.b,p.dered_u,p.dered_g,p.dered_r,p.dered_i,p.dered_z FROM PhotoObj AS p WHERE   (p.dered_u - p.dered_g) > #  AND (p.dered_g - p.dered_r) BETWEEN # AND #  AND (p.dered_u - p.dered_g) BETWEEN # AND #  AND p.l BETWEEN # and #  AND p.b BETWEEN # and #
